ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: For students interested in parasitology this is a good class to take
Great class, would recommend to anyone interested in parasitology
I would strongly recommend this course to other students.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I am in the Immunology track, so this course is not directly applicable, but it does link strongly with immunology in many aspects and it is interesting to look specifically at immunology in response to parasites
Although this course doesn't have too much to do with my current project, but definitely this course helps me understand better of parasites and their interaction between host.
